====================================
 GifBooth README
====================================


Software requirements
--------------------------------------------
 - git-core			# downloading/updating GifBooth
 - gphoto2			# camera tethering software
 - eom				# image viewer
 - mpv				# video player
 - awk				# find eventid for keyboard button
 - sed				# find eventid for keyboard button
 - xmodmap			# remap keyboard button
 - thd				# run script when pressing keyboard button
 - ffmpeg			# video conversion

Install requirements on Debian/Ubuntu
--------------------------------------------
sudo apt-get install git-core gphoto2 eom mpv awk sed xmodmap thd ffmpeg


Getting a working copy
--------------------------------------------
 - git clone https://github.com/theboothbrothers/GifBooth.git


Cleaning the working copy
--------------------------------------------
 1) remove any new files you added (config files and images are ignored)
	git clean -df

 2) undo any changes you might have done to the source code
	git checkout origin/master -- .


Updating the working copy
--------------------------------------------
 - git pull origin master
